<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Spline_(mathematics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<p><b>Theory</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://math.fullerton.edu/mathews/n2003/CubicSplinesMod.html" class="external text" title="http://math.fullerton.edu/mathews/n2003/CubicSplinesMod.html" rel="nofollow">Cubic Splines Module</a> Prof. John H. Mathews <a href="/wiki/California_State_University,_Fullerton" title="California State University, Fullerton">California State University, Fullerton</a></li>
<li><a href="http://ibiblio.org/e-notes/Splines/Intro.htm" class="external text" title="http://ibiblio.org/e-notes/Splines/Intro.htm" rel="nofollow">An Interactive Introduction to Splines</a>, ibiblio.org</li>
</ul>
<p><b>Online utilities</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.akiti.ca/CubicSpline.html" class="external text" title="http://www.akiti.ca/CubicSpline.html" rel="nofollow">Online Cubic Spline Interpolation Utility</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.vias.org/simulations/simusoft_spline.html" class="external text" title="http://www.vias.org/simulations/simusoft_spline.html" rel="nofollow">Learning by Simulations</a> Interactive simulation of various cubic splines</li>
<li><a href="http://demonstrations.wolfram.com/SymmetricalSplineCurves/" class="external text" title="http://demonstrations.wolfram.com/SymmetricalSplineCurves/" rel="nofollow">Symmetrical Spline Curves</a>, an animation by <a href="/wiki/Theodore_Gray" title="Theodore Gray">Theodore Gray</a>, <a href="/wiki/The_Wolfram_Demonstrations_Project" title="The Wolfram Demonstrations Project" class="mw-redirect">The Wolfram Demonstrations Project</a>, 2007.</li>
</ul>
<p><b>Computer Code</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://numericalmethods.eng.usf.edu/topics/spline_method.html" class="external text" title="http://numericalmethods.eng.usf.edu/topics/spline_method.html" rel="nofollow">Notes, PPT, Mathcad, Maple, Mathematica, Matlab</a>, <i>Holistic Numerical Methods Institute</i></li>
<li><a href="http://w3.pppl.gov/ntcc/PSPLINE/" class="external text" title="http://w3.pppl.gov/ntcc/PSPLINE/" rel="nofollow">various routines</a>, NTCC</li>
<li><a href="http://www.sintef.no/sisl" class="external text" title="http://www.sintef.no/sisl" rel="nofollow">Sisl: Opensource C-library for NURBS</a>, SINTEF</li>
<li><a href="http://www.vbnumericalmethods.com/math/" class="external text" title="http://www.vbnumericalmethods.com/math/" rel="nofollow">VBA Spline Interpolation</a>, vbnumericalmethods.com</li>
</ul>


